{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":817,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120784,"text":"(Whistling ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":124160,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127503,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131600,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":133734,"text":"That was whistling."},{"time":135097,"text":"I'm trying to do this in English."},{"time":139000,"text":"What is a chubby,\ncurly-haired guy from Holland --"},{"time":144231,"text":"why is he whistling?"},{"time":145773,"text":"Well actually, I've been whistling\nsince the age of four, about four."},{"time":149228,"text":"My dad was always whistling\naround the house,"},{"time":151418,"text":"and I just thought that's part\nof communication in my family."},{"time":154509,"text":"So I whistled along with him."},{"time":156232,"text":"And actually, until I was 34,"},{"time":159719,"text":"I always annoyed and irritated\npeople with whistling,"},{"time":164283,"text":"because, to be honest,"},{"time":166000,"text":"my whistling is a kind\nof deviant behavior."},{"time":170309,"text":"I whistled alone,\nI whistled in the classroom,"},{"time":173598,"text":"I whistled on bike, I whistled everywhere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176308,"text":"And I also whistled\nat a Christmas Eve party"},{"time":179712,"text":"with my family-in-law."},{"time":181457,"text":"And they had some, in my opinion,\nterrible Christmas music."},{"time":186163,"text":"And when I hear music that I don't like,\nI try to make it better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189925,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":191331,"text":"So when \"Rudolph the Red-Nosed\nReindeer\" -- you know it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194835,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197765,"text":"But it can also sound like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199491,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202638,"text":"But during a Christmas party --"},{"time":205620,"text":"at dinner, actually -- it's very annoying."},{"time":207857,"text":"So my sister-in-law asked me a few times,\n\"Please stop whistling.\""},{"time":212340,"text":"And I just couldn't."},{"time":213652,"text":"And at one point --"},{"time":214877,"text":"and I had some wine,\nI have to admit that --"},{"time":217113,"text":"at one point I said,\n\"If there was a contest, I would join.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":220412,"text":"And two weeks later,"},{"time":221878,"text":"I received a text message:\n\"You're going to America.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":225310,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":227220,"text":"So, OK, I'm going to America."},{"time":230072,"text":"I would love to, but why?"},{"time":231700,"text":"So I immediately called her up, of course."},{"time":233881,"text":"She googled, and she found\nthis World Whistling Championship"},{"time":238487,"text":"in America, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240288,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":242618,"text":"She didn't expect me to go there."},{"time":245000,"text":"And I would have lost my face."},{"time":248163,"text":"I don't know if that's correct English."},{"time":250173,"text":"But the Dutch people here\nwill understand what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252723,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255206,"text":"I lost my face."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"And she thought, \"He will never go there.\""},{"time":262616,"text":"But actually, I did."},{"time":264226,"text":"So I went to Louisburg, North Carolina,\nsoutheast of the United States,"},{"time":269795,"text":"and I entered the world of whistling."},{"time":272810,"text":"And I also entered the World Championship,"},{"time":275344,"text":"and I won there, in 2004."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":281936,"text":"That was great fun, of course."},{"time":286321,"text":"And to defend my title --\nlike judokas do and sportsmen --"},{"time":291841,"text":"I thought, well let's go back in 2005 --"},{"time":294206,"text":"and I won again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295389,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":296928,"text":"Then I couldn't participate\nfor a few years."},{"time":299049,"text":"And in 2008, I entered again\nin Japan, Tokyo, and I won again."},{"time":303615,"text":"So what happened now"},{"time":306000,"text":"is I'm standing here in Rotterdam,\nin the beautiful city, on a big stage,"},{"time":309840,"text":"and I'm talking about whistling."},{"time":311774,"text":"And actually, I earn my money\nwhistling, at the moment."},{"time":315277,"text":"So I quit my day job as a nurse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"And I try to live my dream --"},{"time":325000,"text":"well, actually, it was never my dream,\nbut it sounds so good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328169,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"OK, I'm not the only one whistling here."},{"time":332317,"text":"You say, \"Huh, what do you mean?\""},{"time":334466,"text":"Well actually, you are going\nto whistle along."},{"time":340476,"text":"And then always the same thing happens:"},{"time":342938,"text":"people are watching each other\nand think, \"Oh, my God."},{"time":345736,"text":"Why? Can I go away?\""},{"time":347914,"text":"No, you can't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349347,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":351846,"text":"Actually, it's very simple."},{"time":353218,"text":"The track that I will whistle\nis called \"FÃªte de la Belle.\""},{"time":357154,"text":"It's about 80 minutes long."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358995,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360424,"text":"No, no, no. It's four minutes long."},{"time":363000,"text":"And I want to first rehearse\nwith you your whistling."},{"time":367167,"text":"Yes, so I whistle the tone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368943,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":371000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":373348,"text":"Sorry, I forgot one thing --"},{"time":376163,"text":"you whistle the same tone as me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378756,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":380629,"text":"I heard a wide variety of tones."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386790,"text":"(Geert Chatrou and audience whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400099,"text":"(Whistling ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":401329,"text":"This is very promising."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402712,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":403923,"text":"This is very promising."},{"time":405288,"text":"I'll ask the technicians\nto start the music."},{"time":408000,"text":"And if it's started,\nI just point where you whistle along,"},{"time":411262,"text":"and we will see what happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412859,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":418623,"text":"Oh, I'm so sorry, technicians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422670,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":426923,"text":"I'm so used to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":428145,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429193,"text":"I start it myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":430542,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431727,"text":"OK, here it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436373,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438343,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":449108,"text":"(Whistling ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":450283,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454322,"text":"OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456426,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":503819,"text":"It's easy, isn't it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506000,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540349,"text":"Now comes the solo,\nI propose I do that myself, OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":543373,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":546000,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":679000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":690000,"text":"Max Westerman: Geert Chatrou,\nthe World Champion of Whistling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693753,"text":"Geert Chatrou: Thank you. Thank you."}]}]}